creator: Julia Caroline Dorr
description:
LibriVox recording of Friar Anselmo, and Other Poems by Julia Caroline Dorr.
Read in English by Chris Pyle; Julia Layne; Ezwa; Ken Masters; Carol; DomBombadil; Vetta; Shakira Searle; KHand; Kristin Gjerløw; Algy Pug; Larry Wilson; Newgatenovelist; J. McDougall
This is a collection of poems by Julia Caroline Dorr. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
